    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2>사용 환경</h2>

<hr />

<ul>
<li>모델명    :     MacBook Pro</li>
<li>모델 식별자:   MacBookPro8,1</li>
<li>메모리:           4 GB</li>
<li>Eclipse: v4.2.1</li>
</ul>


<h2>요구 환경</h2>

<hr />

<ul>
<li>Eclipse 3.4+</li>
</ul>


<h3>Eclipse Classic 설치</h3>

<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.eclipse.org/downloads/">Eclipse Classic</a>를 다운 받습니다.</li>
</ul>


<p><img src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-eEEddA1zCKw/UK9H_HFMlMI/AAAAAAAAADM/apX-8h1nAGE/%25252FUsers%25252Fhancho%25252FPictures%25252Feeclipse-down-classic.jpg" width="500" height="500" title="&#34;Eclipse down&#34;" alt="&#34;Eclipse down&#34;"></p>

<ul>
<li><p>다운 받은 파일은 .tar.gz 압축 파일 이므로 압축 해제후 Eclipse 아이콘을 클릭 합니다.</p></li>
<li><p>실행을 이어 나가면 다음과 같은 페이지가 나오며 'ok'를 클릭 합니다.</p></li>
</ul>


<p><img src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-GlTWPfVPvs0/UK9I7Ea48yI/AAAAAAAAADU/Isd5LGHAKGo/%25252FUsers%25252Fhancho%25252FPictures%25252Feclipse-install-01.jpg" width="500" height="500" title="&#34;Eclipse 설치&#34;" alt="&#34;Eclipse 설치&#34;"></p>

<ul>
<li>설치 완료</li>
</ul>


<h3>Android SDK 설치</h3>

<ul>
<li><a href="http://developer.android.com/sdk/index.html">SDK</a>에서 다운로드 가능 합니다.</li>
</ul>


<p><img src="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-4Kryzuug_wA/UK9KTEltWAI/AAAAAAAAADc/Ci-vVNhUJC0/%25252FUsers%25252Fhancho%25252FPictures%25252Fphoone%25252Fphone-android-01.jpg" width="500" height="500" title="&#34;SDK Down&#34;" alt="&#34;SDK Down&#34;"></p>

<h3>Android SDK 환경 설정</h3>

<p>파일 열기</p>

<pre><code>$ vi ~/.bash_profile
</code></pre>

<p>.bash_profile 자신이 다운 받은 SDK파일의 경로를 추가해 줍니다.</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>bash_profile </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>export PATH=${PATH}:/Development/android-sdk-macosx/platform-tools:/Development/android-sdk-macosx/tools</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p>설정 확인</p>

<pre><code>$ source ~/.bash_profile
$ echo $PATH
…./Users/han/Development/android-sdk-macosx/sdk/platform-tools:/Users/han/Development/android-sdk-macosx/tools….
</code></pre>

<h3>Xcode Command Line Tools 설치</h3>

<h5>Xcode 실행후 > Xcode Preferences 선택 합니다.</h5>

<p><img src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-9lGHtlIr6t0/UK3bfp3Kn9I/AAAAAAAAACc/7g0GBCw6L24/%25252FUsers%25252Fhancho%25252FPictures%25252Fxcode-line-tool-01.jpg" width="500" height="500" title="&#34;Command line 설치&#34;" alt="&#34;Command line 설치&#34;"></p>

<h5>Downloads->Components-> Command Line Tools -> Install 클릭으로 설치 합니다.</h5>

<p><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-rAUx02VExcY/UK3br16WT8I/AAAAAAAAACk/1b5_-hdFebk/%25252FUsers%25252Fhancho%25252FPictures%25252Fxcode-line-tool-02.jpg" width="500" height="500" title="&#34;Command Line Tolls 설치&#34;" alt="&#34;Command Line Tolls 설치&#34;"></p>

<p>설치가 끝나면 Terminal.app (iTerm)에서 커맨드 라인으로 작업을 할수가 있습니다. 자세한 사항은
<a href="http://docs.phonegap.com/en/2.2.0/guide_command-line_index.md.html#Command-Line%20Usage">Command-Line</a>에서 iOS 부분을 참고 하시면 됩니다.</p>

<h3>Apache Cordova 다운로드</h3>

<p>다운로드된 파일은 .zip 파일이므로 압축을 풀어서 사용하시면 됩니다.</p>

<ul>
<li>Cordova는 <a href="http://phonegap.com/download">Cordova-Down</a>에서 다운 받을수 있습니다.</li>
<li>다운 받은 폴더를 ~/CordovaLib-2.x.x 쓰기 편한 위치로 이동 시킵니다.</li>
</ul>


<h3>새로운 프로젝트 시작하기</h3>

<h5>bin 폴더 열기</h5>

<p>새로운 프로젝트를 생성하기 위해서는 ./create 파일을 실행 해야 합니다. create 파일은
lib/android/bin 폴더에 존재 합니다.</p>

<ul>
<li>lib/ios/bin 폴더로 직접 이동 해서 사용할수 있습니다.</li>
<li>~/CordovalLib-2.2/lib/android/bin 폴더를 Terminal.app에 드래그 하면 bin 폴더로 바로 이동 할수 있습니다.</li>
</ul>


<h5>create 실행하기</h5>

<pre><code>$ ./create &lt;project_folder_path&gt; &lt;package_name&gt; &lt;project_name&gt;

$ ./create &lt;project_folder_path&gt; pheonegap.start start
$ cd ~/project_folder_path
$ ls

AndroidManifest.xml cordova   project.properties
ant.properties                gen           res
assets                        libs          src
bin                           local.properties
build.xml                     proguard-project.txt
</code></pre>

<h3>Simulator 실행하기</h3>

<h4>SDK 지정 하기</h4>

<p>eclipse를 처음 실행 하게 되면 다음과 같이 SDK 폴더를 지정합니다.</p>

<p><img src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-ot4Vk-4u5_Y/ULLcJlNDr9I/AAAAAAAAADs/5Vx_AyDGqRo/%25252FUsers%25252Fhancho%25252FPictures%25252Fphoone%25252FSDK-file-mv.jpg" width="500" height="500" title="&#34;SDK 지정&#34;" alt="&#34;SDK 지정&#34;"></p>

<p>SDK 경로 수정은 'Command + ,' 사용해서 열수 있습니다.</p>

<h4>Android SDK 매니저 설치</h4>

<p>Android SDK 매니저 버튼을 클릭하거나 'Window -> Android SDK Mannager'를 클릭 합니다.</p>

<p><img src="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-faBm7F2Gk0U/ULLhaJEOVKI/AAAAAAAAAD8/ei5iS_wI_C8/%25252FUsers%25252Fhancho%25252FPictures%25252FAndroid-sdk-man-01.jpg" width="100" height="100" title="&#34;Android SDK Mannager&#34;" alt="&#34;Android SDK Mannager&#34;"></p>

<h4>SDK 패키지 선택</h4>

<p>버전에 맞는 API 선택하고 install package 버튼을 클릭 합니다.</p>

<p><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-BpJep0rpajw/ULLidv8yTeI/AAAAAAAAAEE/fP0unxE902w/%25252FUsers%25252Fhancho%25252FPictures%25252Fphoone%25252FSDK-select.jpg" width="500" height="500" title="&#34;패키지 선택&#34;" alt="&#34;패키지 선택&#34;"></p>

<h4>SDK 패키지 설치</h4>

<p>체크된 패키지를 설치 합니다.</p>

<p><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-Lpn5YCOcQyM/ULLjgqCa5WI/AAAAAAAAAEM/PmE7fb1xD2E/%25252FUsers%25252Fhancho%25252FPictures%25252Fphoone%25252FSDK-install.jpg" width="500" height="500" title="&#34;패키지 설치&#34;" alt="&#34;패키지 설치&#34;"></p>

<h4>Android ADK Plugin 설치</h4>

<p><a href="http://developer.android.com/sdk/installing/installing-adt.html">ADK Plugin</a>에서 다운 받고 설치 가이드를 확인 할수 있습니다.</p>

<h4>ADK 설치</h4>

<h5>Help -> insall new software를 클릭 합니다.</h5>

<p><img src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-QR5gGvGIngA/ULLoh0ZOI4I/AAAAAAAAAEc/tL9uY_4jPxE/%25252FUsers%25252Fhancho%25252FPictures%25252Fphoone%25252Fphonegap-eclipse-ADT-01.png" width="500" height="500" title="&#34;install ADK&#34;" alt="&#34;install ADK&#34;"></p>

<h5>화면 오른쪽 위에 'add' 클릭</h5>

<p><img src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-0NJRgGDaZJM/ULLo4vEJUzI/AAAAAAAAAEk/824uJ-URvMo/%25252FUsers%25252Fhancho%25252FPictures%25252Fphoone%25252Fphonegap-eclipse-ADT-02.png" width="500" height="500" title="&#34;클릭 Add&#34;" alt="&#34;클릭 Add&#34;"></p>

<h5>Add Repository 설정</h5>

<p>Location에서 문제가 발생하면 'https' 'http'를 사용하도록 합니다.</p>

<pre><code>Name: ADT Plugin
Location: https://dl-ssl.google.com/android/eclipse/
</code></pre>

<p><img src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-756En0wgbWg/ULLpdkrdeyI/AAAAAAAAAEs/tvSMuwiWP2o/%25252FUsers%25252Fhancho%25252FPictures%25252Fphoone%25252Fphonegap-eclipse-ADT-03.png" width="500" height="500" title="&#34;Add Repository 설정&#34;" alt="&#34;Add Repository 설정&#34;"></p>

<h5>Available Software</h5>

<p>Developer Tools과 필요한 프로그램을 클릭 한뒤 Next를 클릭합니다.</p>

<p><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-gregw6cQ3dg/ULLqQ4ptnsI/AAAAAAAAAE0/5Z_M_28kDto/%25252FUsers%25252Fhancho%25252FPictures%25252Fphoone%25252Fphonegap-eclipse-ADT-04.png" width="500" height="500" title="&#34;Software 선택&#34;" alt="&#34;Software 선택&#34;"></p>

<h5>Install Details</h5>

<p>인스톨 되는 정보를 확인후 'Next'를 클릭 합니다.</p>

<p><img src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-52_7il-K0S8/ULLrXNkRVLI/AAAAAAAAAE8/qN-lTWrhHhM/%25252FUsers%25252Fhancho%25252FPictures%25252Fphoone%25252Fphonegap-eclipse-ADT-05.png" width="500" height="500" title="&#34;Show Details&#34;" alt="&#34;Show Details&#34;"></p>

<h5>Review Lienses</h5>

<p>라이센스 확인후 'Finish'를 클릭 합니다.</p>

<p><img src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-Yv_t0AQWpA0/ULLsKWQ2S-I/AAAAAAAAAFE/HwgarHXkDh0/%25252FUsers%25252Fhancho%25252FPictures%25252Fphoone%25252Fphonegap-eclipse-ADT-06.png" width="500" height="500" title="&#34;Finish click&#34;" alt="&#34;Finish click&#34;"></p>

<h5>Security Warning</h5>

<p>경고 화면이 나오게 되면 'Ok'를 클릭 하도록 합니다.</p>

<p><img src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-6yjCMs_WoVE/ULLsmN2bdCI/AAAAAAAAAFM/X7PlH385Prw/%25252FUsers%25252Fhancho%25252FPictures%25252Fphoone%25252Fphonegap-eclipse-ADT-07.png" width="500" height="500" title="&#34;Security Warning&#34;" alt="&#34;Security Warning&#34;"></p>

<h5>Software Update</h5>

<p>설치가 끝나면 'Yes'를 클릭하여 새로 eclipse를 시작 하도록 합니다.</p>

<p><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-HzGam6KOJLE/ULLtUTbrgDI/AAAAAAAAAFU/bk2nSeaO2ns/%25252FUsers%25252Fhancho%25252FPictures%25252Fphoone%25252Fphonegap-eclipse-ADT-08.png" width="500" height="500" title="&#34;Software Update&#34;" alt="&#34;Software Update&#34;"></p>

<h3>ADV(Android Virtual Device Manager)</h3>

<p> ADV 버튼을 클릭하거나 'Window -> Anroid Virtual Devie Manger'를 클릭 합니다.</p>

<p> <img src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-nObeGIzAtuc/ULLw2ta5CII/AAAAAAAAAFk/SO4WnHg0130/%25252FUsers%25252Fhancho%25252FPictures%25252FADV.jpg" width="80" height="80" title="&#34;ADV&#34;" alt="&#34;ADV&#34;"></p>

<h5>ADV New</h5>

<p>오른쪽 상단에 'New' 버튼을 클릭 합니다.</p>

<p><img src="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-WgSKxxkSptI/ULLzFef9chI/AAAAAAAAAFs/YTf6Lq27rzA/%25252FUsers%25252Fhancho%25252FPictures%25252FADV-New.jpg" width="300" height="300" title="&#34;ADV New&#34;" alt="&#34;ADV New&#34;"></p>

<h5>ADV Create</h5>

<p>ADV 이름과 Device를 선택후 'ok'를 누릅니다.</p>

<p><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-aY9paQ9DKgY/ULLzyLaMHyI/AAAAAAAAAF0/Fc5g96lajm4/%25252FUsers%25252Fhancho%25252FPictures%25252FADV-name.jpg" width="300" height="300" title="&#34;ADV Create&#34;" alt="&#34;ADV Create&#34;"></p>

<h3>Eclipse 실행</h3>

<ul>
<li>Command line tools를 사용 하여 새로운 프로젝트를 만듭니다.</li>
<li>다운 받은 eclipse폴더에서 eclipse를 실행 합니다.</li>
<li>eclipse에서 'File->New->Project'를 클릭 합니다.</li>
<li>New Project 창에서 'Android Project from Existing Code'선택후 'Next'를 클릭 합니다.</li>
<li>우측 상단의 'Browse..' 클릭후 생성된 Cordova 프로젝트폴더를 엽니다.</li>
<li>Root Directory 정의후 'Run'실행 후 ADV를 선택 해주면 Android화면이생성</li>
<li>Phonegap Android는 컴파일 시간이 오래 걸리므로 기다려 주어야 합니다.</li>
</ul>


